         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Toorak ¶ 24th July 1861 ¶ My dear Dr Mueller, ¶  ¶ I return your letter to Sir William Hooker. ¶ M to W. Hooker, 23 July 1861. ¶  ¶ I think your offer in regard to Mr Bentham's proposed Flora of Austr...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">61.07.24a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Henry Barkly</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Directors' letters, vol. LXXV, Australian and Pacific letters 1859-65, letter no. 12.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>MS black-edged.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>T<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">his is presumably the letter from Barkly that M enclosed with the letter he wrote to William Hooker on 25 July 1861 (in the edition as 61-07-25a).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Toorak</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">24th July 1861</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Dr Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I return your letter to Sir William Hooker.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to W. Hooker, 23 July 1861.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I think your offer in regard to Mr Bentham's proposed Flora of Australia is most generous and liberal, &amp; I will give it every support in writing to Sir William.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See H. Barkly to W. Hooker 24 July 1861<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as M61-07-24).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am too busy at the moment in preparing for the Mail to say more.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have read the letters which you kindly encl[osed] &amp; send them back with thanks.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letters not identified.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">[Ever] [faithfully]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Henry Barkly.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
